{"tid":1604940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Donald Trump公開支持《中英聯合聲明》, 香港人都唔應該放棄","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T07:05:05.000Z","uid":134071,"like":60,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"935cf926cfdd2e194751023d5bff427b78e456bc","tid":1604940,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:31:14.000Z","msg":"特朗普之前已經係G7簽名支持《中英聯合聲明》, &nbsp;而且仲開口講埋支持《中英聯合聲明》<br />\n<br />\n美國支持香港人既行動, 都係基於《中英聯合聲明》. &nbsp; <br />\n如果《中英聯合聲明》玩完, 美國支持香港人既行動就無左一個基礎.  <br />\n所以, 香港人而家唔應該放棄《中英聯合聲明》.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BFZ2meIBUlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBFZ2meIBUlE&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1QxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=bdec0e36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BFZ2meIBUlE</a>"},{"pid":"34e1312f1c4ba343d1083e21bb168ca81d37a5c1","tid":1604940,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:31:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10156235616821121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffokguy%2Fposts%2F10156235616821121&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1QxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=8cff7c14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10156235616821121</a><br />\n<br />\nKay Lam<br />\n9月25日 19:02 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n中國一向自稱不承認三條「不平等條約」，因此廢除聯合聲明，都不代表中國會交還香港，而係中國從此做乜都得；<strong>所以「廢除聯合聲明」，係變相幫香港自殺</strong>－－美英一直都係以聯合聲明來作為撐香港的理據<br />\n<br />\n除非係說服美國出兵，而廢除不代表美國出兵，錯晒因果"},{"pid":"4205d5b2cf8439ebf7a926edea7a5ff1f146f1ef","tid":1604940,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>特朗普之前已經係G7簽名支持《中英聯合聲明》,  而<strong>家</strong>仲開口講埋支持《中英聯合聲明》<br />\n<br />\n美國支持香港人既行動, 都係基於《中英聯合聲明》.   <br />\n如果《中英聯合聲明》玩完, 美國支持香港人既行動就無左一個基礎.  <br />\n所以, 香港人而家唔應該放棄《中英聯合聲明》.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BFZ2meIBUlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBFZ2meIBUlE&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1QxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=bdec0e36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BFZ2meIBUlE</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"69169157547a46922cf8213299f637dcfeaebd07","tid":1604940,"uid":36086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">午安01同志</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n大家幫推聯署丫<br />\n請美國政府行使《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁親中人士。(DL: Oct/10）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/global-magnitsky-act-pro-beijing-officials-hong-kong-executive-council\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fglobal-magnitsky-act-pro-beijing-officials-hong-kong-executive-council&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1QxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=a671ad07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/global-magnitsky-act-pro-beijing-officials-hong-kong-executive-council</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國國會禁止香港警察移民或入境美國（DL: Oct/18）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-impose-sanctions-hong-kong-police-until-all-have-committed-state-terrorism-crimes-are-brought-justice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-impose-sanctions-hong-kong-police-until-all-have-committed-state-terrorism-crimes-are-brought-justice&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1QxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=99fdb45b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-impose-sanctions-hong-kong-police-until-all-have-committed-state-terrorism-crimes-are-brought-justice</a><br />\n<br />\n簽＞收電郵＞確認簽署＞廣傳</strong></span>"},{"pid":"fa5eda72fc9e70f312a55db3ad200d05336f43d6","tid":1604940,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB